menu "NeuroSync Pro bench options"

config NSP_BENCH_SYNC_40HZ
    bool "Bench-only 40 Hz sync output on GPIO19"
    default n
    help
        Enables a bench image that drives NSP_GPIO_SYNC (GPIO19) with a
        hardware-timed 40.000 Hz, 50% duty MCPWM square wave after the
        firmware reaches SAFE.

        This is not production firmware. GPIO23 output-enable remains low,
        and all non-sync outputs remain in the safe-low list.

endmenu
